<div class="title">Memory Loss</div>
<div class="substance">Alprazolam (Xanax)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Cyan&Exact=1">Cyan</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Cyan. "Memory Loss: An Experience with Alprazolam (Xanax) (exp34409)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 20, 2006. erowid.org/exp/34409</div>

